{"tid":633072,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【靈魂出竅?】《櫻桃小丸子》罕見擺烏龍 同框驚現兩個嫲嫲","createTime":"2018-04-18T03:37:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-18T05:22:34.000Z","uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"193e57ce081eb54a7e3476872edc6339c309dfa0","tid":633072,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T03:37:35.000Z","msg":"2018-04-1624.2K<br />\n即時娛樂<br />\n <img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180416/large/1523846826_d9e8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180416%2Flarge%2F1523846826_d9e8.jpg&h=9d1d207b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《櫻桃小丸子》昨日發生罕見擺烏龍，同框驚現兩個嫲嫲。<br />\n<br />\n呢幕講嫲嫲行去轉台。<br />\n<br />\n轉完台之後....<br />\n<br />\n鏡頭一轉，竟然出現兩個嫲嫲。<br />\n【新增回應】<br />\n富士電視台嘅長壽電視動畫《櫻桃小丸子》，從90年代播到o依家，可謂橫跨咗幾代嘅觀眾，絕對係大人細路嘅美好回憶。<br />\n<br />\n不過，《櫻桃小丸子》噚日喺日本播出嘅最新一集卻發生「靈異事件」，唔少觀眾都發現同一個畫面竟然同時間出現兩個嫲嫲，繼而引起網民喺社交網洗板式討論。<br />\n<br />\n呢集劇情交代到小丸子一家爭睇電視，本來坐低嘅嫲嫲就起身行埋電視機轉台，點知鏡頭一轉，嫲嫲企喺電視旁邊嘅同時，原位仍然見到另一個嫲嫲坐喺度，仲同其他家人一樣，對「自己」轉台呢個舉動用滴汗來表達出無奈之情。其實出現兩個嫲嫲，好明顯係製作單位出現罕見嘅擺烏龍情況，由於日本節目甚少出現呢類致命性嘅失誤，唔少網民都議論紛紛，有人疑問係咪刻意加入嘅恐怖元素，亦有指劇情可能交代嫲嫲一直係對「孖妹」，仲話佢可能識得靈魂出竅。<br />\n<br />\n及至今日，電視台方面對於今次失誤已作出道歉，並回應指係作畫上出錯，表示今後製作時會加倍注意。"},{"pid":"52c53364ff0f89b2b59af7fa4d8cfa02bd62e5d4","tid":633072,"uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T03:38:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20180416/58079001\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180416%2F58079001&d=iV%2BIcVmtk%2BfJ2CliG5mnCE%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=271df54c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180416%2F58079001&h=946b3c02\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20180416/58079001</a>"},{"pid":"14ae47d1456e7e3beb728019a7b68a2540c8cb73","tid":633072,"uid":37524,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T03:39:57.000Z","msg":"你2019先出post啦<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/631195/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/631195/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"9d0b6bb63461a09c8e7f2b8b145eb0e0620f64d7","tid":633072,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T04:35:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"514637b62b1bfcf0d6b81ed3881cd90d76aac68c","tid":633072,"uid":1067,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T04:53:03.000Z","msg":"食孖妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af0d49a303e655fb7e0d02de41c70150c1d284f4","tid":633072,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T05:22:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}